result.title: Looking for interested innovators
result.content:
Currently me and my friends are working on a couple of real-life projects (not only competitive programming-related), and I’m looking for more interested people to join us make apps, websites, and hugh-potential startups! You can share your ideas with us, and we can work on them! Because by joining us, you’re a part of us. We’re based in Cambridge, Massachusetts, United States, but in 21st century distance can’t limit us, because we’re connected 24/7.

If you’re interested, send me a message. iOS, Android, React Native, back-end and front-end developers get a +
